<h2 id="experience">Experience</h2>

<p><span style="color:rgb(34,34,34)"><strong>iOS Developer</strong></span>  <br />
<span style="color:rgb(34,34,34)"><em>Jan 2018 - Present</em></span></p>

<p>I have created many apps and games for education, accessibility, wellness and fun. Check out <a href="/apps">my apps</a>.</p>

<p><span style="color:rgb(34,34,34)"><strong>Summer Intern</strong></span>  <br />
<span style="color:rgb(34,34,34)"><em>CESAR - Instituto de Inovação — Recife, Brazil, Jan - Feb 2019</em></span></p>

<p>During the summer job program at <a href="https://www.cesar.org.br/">CESAR</a>, I developed a cognitive stimulating virtual reality game for people who suffer dementia.</p>

<p><span style="color:rgb(34,34,34)"><strong>Photographer</strong></span>  <br />
<span style="color:rgb(34,34,34)"><em>Holocaust Museum — Haifa, Israel, Jun - Jul 2016</em></span></p>

<p>Throughout the time I volunteered at <a href="https://yadezer.org.il/?lang=en">Yad Ezer La’Haver</a>, I was able to photograph dozens of holocaust survivors and document their stories. Currently, the photographs I took are part of the permanent exhibition of the museum.</p>

